window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Gaea's favored children have put her ancient plan to cleanse the Earth of humans into motion, and Kozalin stands high on their list of targets. Uncertain alliances, scheming gods, and an implacable foe will push Daniel to his limits. How far will the wizard from Earth go to protect his family? </p> <p>Warning: This novel contains graphic violence, explicit sex, unconventional opinions and a protagonist who has no interest in being normal. Listen at your own risk. </p>"; 
